## Install Plasma Meta along with related kde-apps
*kde-plasma/plasma-meta
## $$ Make absolutely sure we have wayland compositor (kwin)
*kde-plasma/kwin

## ## Administrative utilities, which help in managing the system.
*kde-apps/kdeadmin-meta
## $$ Basic applications such as file browser, editor, terminal emulator.
*kde-apps/kdecore-meta

